Fixes: e305509e678b ("Bluetooth: use correct lock to prevent UAF of hdev object")
Acked-by: Luiz Augusto von Dentz <luiz.von.dentz@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Linus Torvalds <torvalds@linux-foundation.org>
